ZH: 我们要携手共进，共同创造更美好的未来。
EN: We need to work hand in hand to create a better future together.

ZH: 我们应该携手合作，共同解决这个问题。
EN: We should collaborate and work together to solve this problem.

ZH: 只有携手同心，我们才能取得成功。
EN: Only by joining hands and working together can we achieve success.

ZH: 他们携手游览了整个城市。
EN: They explored the entire city hand in hand.

ZH: 两国元首共同携手，促进双边关系的发展。
EN: The heads of the two countries joined hands to promote the development of bilateral relations.

